Intro:
------
Creates a deploy directory as outlined in the mongrel2 manual. Mainly used to quickly setup some test servers. More or less follows the Deploying section of the mongrel2 manual: http://mongrel2.org/static/mongrel2-manual.html#x1-410004

How to use:
-----------
1. Download the files.
2. Edit deploy and run if you do not want to deploy in ~/Code
3. Open up a terminal and run chmod u+x deploy
4. Open up a terminal and run chmod u+x run
5. ./deploy
6. ./run

